# act configuration — runs .github/workflows/*.yml locally against
# Docker-backed GitHub Actions runners.  See docs/development/CI_LOCAL.md.
#
# Pinned image: catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest is the "medium" image
# from the act project's curated list — ~5 GB, includes most common
# build tools (curl, git, gh, jq, python, node).  The default act
# image (`node:16-buster-slim`) is too minimal for our workflows,
# while the "full" 18-GB image is overkill.
#
# Bind to linux/amd64 explicitly so Apple Silicon hosts get reproducible
# behavior (otherwise act invokes arm64 runners which may behave
# differently from GHA's amd64 runners).
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest
--container-architecture linux/amd64
